# ============================================================
# AI-SUCE — Monorepo Environment Reference
#
# Each app manages its own environment. Use the per-app .env.example files:
#   apps/api/.env.example                → Backend
#   apps/web-greenpurse/.env.example    → GreenPurse frontend
#   apps/web-greensc/.env.example       → GreenSC frontend
#   apps/web-admin/.env.example         → Admin dashboard
#   apps/web-virtualfarm/.env.example   → MyVirtualFarm frontend
#
# The root .env is the SHARED running config for local monorepo development
# (backend + all frontends). It is NOT used in production.
# ============================================================

# Root .env is the LOCAL development config — NOT a deployment reference.
# See DEPLOYMENT.md for production deployment instructions.
# See apps/*/.env.example for per-app production env vars.